body:
`facet` has the following syntax:

```javascript
{
  "$searchMeta"|"$search": {
    "index": <index name>, // optional, defaults to "default"
    "facet": {
      "operator": {
        <operator-specifications>
      },
      "facets": {
        <facet-definitions>
      }
    },
    "returnScope": {
      "path": "<embedded-documents-field-to-query>"
    },
    "returnStoredSource": true
  }
}
```
